Philip is a
motivational speaker.

00:00:21.830 --> 00:00:23.100 align:middle line:90%
He is an author.

00:00:23.100 --> 00:00:23.910 align:middle line:90%
He is a filmmaker.

00:00:23.910 --> 00:00:28.430 align:middle line:84%
